Oil:
BP’s annual energy outlook 2035:
1) US shale oil production growth likely to slow down in coming years;
2) Pressure on OPEC is likely to persist over the next few years;
3) Global energy demand to grow by 37% over next 20 years;
4) US likely to become self-sufficient in oil by 2030s;
5) Global oil and other liquids demand to grow by 19mn bpd to reach 111mn bpd by 2035;
6) China to overtake US as world's largest oil consumer by 2035.

